= couch example wiki - couch_potato implementation =

(probably requires couchdb trunk, couchrest trunk as of 2009-03-15)


* built-in dirty tracking - handy for versions
* built-in associations, nice for simple associations
* access to creating/querying views via ViewQuery class
* built-in versioning - nice idea but pretty useless because doing it yourself is dead easy
* no sorting - bad
* overly smart view querying gets in your way